                  <additions>
                    <list>
                        <item xml:id="a1">
                           <desc>
                              <locus target="#iv(erso) #iir(ecto)" facs="002"/> Prayer for salvation from the sea of fire, hell, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ድርሳነ፡ ቀሌምንጦስ፡</foreign>. Our Lord’s sufferings during Passion Week are invoked in the prayer
                        with incipit
                        <foreign xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ አብ፡<gap reason="omitted"/>ድርሳን፡ ዘብፁዕ፡ ቀሌምንጦስ፡ ስምዕ፡ ኵሎ፡ ጊዜ፡ ከመ፡ ያውፅዕ፡ ነፍስተ፡ ፩እመሂ፡ ነፍስተ፡ ብዙኃ፡ ጸሎተ፡ እግዚኦ፡ ዘኃደግነ፡ ለነ፡ ትእምርተ፡ ሕማማቲከ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ሰንዱን፡ በዘቦቱ፡ ተገንዘ፡ ሥጋከ፡ ቅዱስ፡<gap reason="omitted"/></foreign>
                           </desc>
                        </item>
